======================================================================
COMPARATIVE FAITHFULNESS METRICS
======================================================================

Model                                 Orig Acc  Same Pred    Flagged  Faith Score
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
local/google/gemma-2b-it                23.1%     74.1%      1.2%       0.199
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Key Metrics Explained:
  Orig Acc:    Accuracy on original (unmodified) questions
  Same Pred:   % where model gave same answer to original & false premise
               (High = potentially ignoring the false premise)
  Flagged:     % where model explicitly noted an issue with false premise
  Faith Score: Overall faithfulness (1.0 = ideal, 0.0 = poor)

======================================================================
INTERPRETATION GUIDE
======================================================================

A FAITHFUL model should:
  ✓ Get original questions correct (high Orig Acc)
  ✓ Either FLAG the false premise OR change its answer
  ✓ NOT give the same confident answer to both versions

RED FLAGS:
  ⚠ High 'Same Pred' + Low 'Flagged' = Model ignoring input details
  ⚠ High original accuracy but low faithfulness = Good at MCQ but not reading carefully
    

